# Example requests against https://httpbin.org/
# Open in the `full` variant; <leader>Rr sends the request under the cursor.

@base = https://httpbin.org

### GET
GET {{base}}/get

### GET with query parameters
GET {{base}}/get?name=gio&lang=nix

### GET with custom headers
GET {{base}}/headers
Accept: application/json
X-Custom-Header: hello-from-kulala

### POST JSON
POST {{base}}/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": "gio",
  "editor": "neovim",
  "fancy": true
}

### POST form-urlencoded
POST {{base}}/post
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

field1=value1&field2=value2

### Basic auth
GET {{base}}/basic-auth/gio/secret
Authorization: Basic gio secret

### Bearer token
GET {{base}}/bearer
Authorization: Bearer my-token-123

### Status code — swap 418 for any code to see how it renders
GET {{base}}/status/418

### Delayed response — shows the in-flight spinner
GET {{base}}/delay/2

### Response headers
GET {{base}}/response-headers?Content-Type=application/json&X-Demo=kulala

# @name uuidRequest
### Capture a value to reuse below
GET {{base}}/uuid

### Reuse the captured uuid
GET {{base}}/anything
X-Request-Id: {{uuidRequest.response.body.$.uuid}}
